  File                     = {R{\"o}diger et al. - 2013 - A highly versatile microscope imaging technology p.pdf:/home/tux/Work/Literatur/Zotero\_DB/zotero/storage/WR6IVT9D/R{\"o}diger et al. - 2013 - A highly versatile microscope imaging technology p.pdf:application/pdf},
